name: IN ENCHANTED WOODS
description: PRAYER, A DIALOGUE WITH ONE'S ALTER EGO, CONSTITUTES A TECHNIQUE OF THE MOST EFFICIENT APPROACH TO THE REALIZATION OF THOSE RESERVE POWERS OF NATURE WHICH ARE STORED AND CONSERVED IN THE UNCONSCIOUS REALMS OF OUR MINDS. WHEN TRAVELING THROUGH UNCHARTERED TERRITORY, LIL PUP RELIES HEAVILY ON THE POWER OF PRAYER
